&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://ita.org.za/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;The ITA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
